  <ThreatReward_Manhunters_Joiner.LetterTextChasing.slateRef>{BASETEXT}\n\n[manhunterArrivalLetterEnd]</ThreatReward_Manhunters_Joiner.LetterTextChasing.slateRef>
  
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->[introduction] named [joiner_nameDef] is calling from nearby. [joiner_pronoun] is begging to join you at [map_definite].[joiner_relationInfo]\n\nThere's some kind of threat following [joiner_nameDef], but [joiner_pronoun] is unwilling to say what it is or when it might follow. [joiner_pronoun] is also unwilling to tell you more about [joiner_objective]self.</li>
    <li>introduction(childCount==1,priority=1)->A [joiner_age]-year-old child</li>
    <li>introduction->A [joiner_age]-year-old [joiner_title]</li>
  -->
  <ThreatReward_MysteryThreat_Joiner.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription->[introduction] يُدعى [joiner_nameDef] يتصل من مكان قريب. يتوسل [joiner_pronoun] للانضمام إليك في [map_definite].[joiner_relationInfo]\n\nهناك نوع من التهديد يتبع [joiner_nameDef]، لكن [joiner_pronoun] غير راغب في قول ماهيته أو متى قد يتبعه. كما أن [joiner_pronoun] غير راغب في إخبارك المزيد عن نفس[joiner_objective].</li>
    <li>introduction(childCount==1,priority=1)->طفل عمره [joiner_age] عاماً</li>
    <li>introduction->[joiner_title] عمره [joiner_age] عاماً</li>
 </ThreatReward_MysteryThreat_Joiner.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
